<h1>About {{ site.title }}</h1>
<p>The Retrofit Key provides unbiased, hands-on reviews of smart retrofit door locks that transform traditional deadbolts into connected entry systems. We test each lock's installation process, app functionality, security features, and compatibility with existing door hardware across diverse home environments. Our evaluations focus on real-world performance, helping homeowners and renters make informed decisions without replacing entire lock systems. We prioritize practical insights over marketing hype, examining battery life, connectivity reliability, and whether these devices truly deliver on their convenience promises.</p>
<p style="color: var(--muted); font-size: 14px; margin-top: 30px;">
Reviews on this site synthesize publicly available research and reflect one perspective on each product.
Scoring categories and weights are chosen per product to fit what matters for that item.
</p>
